sentence: People who believe these incubators drive innovation are kidding themselves, hanya menipu diri sendiri!
This incubator is just a cash grab, not a real support for startups, hanya mencari keuntungan!
Anyone who invests here is just enabling a cycle of tech mediocrity, mendukung siklus mediokritas teknologi!
This place is more about hype than actual technological advancement, lebih banyak hype daripada kemajuan teknologi sebenarnya!
The startups here are doomed to fail due to lack of proper guidance, gagal karena kurangnya bimbingan yang tepat!
Only naive entrepreneurs would get fooled by the shallow promises of this incubator, hanya pengusaha naif yang tertipu!
Supporting this incubator means wasting precious resources on doomed ventures, membuang sumber daya berharga!
I can’t respect anyone who takes this tech incubator seriously, yang menganggap serius inkubator teknologi ini!
It’s appalling how this place claims to foster innovation when it only fosters greed, hanya mendorong keserakahan!
Whoever funds this incubator is just feeding the tech bubble, hanya memberi makan gelembung teknologi!
This incubator’s method is outdated and ineffective, metodenya usang dan tidak efektif!
Every session here is just a parade of buzzwords and no substance, parade kata-kata buzz tanpa substansi!
Their mentorship is superficial and lacks any real depth, pembimbingan yang dangkal dan tanpa kedalaman!
Real tech visionaries would never associate with such a superficial incubator, tidak akan pernah berhubungan dengan inkubator yang dangkal!
The leadership here is clueless about the actual challenges of the tech industry, tidak tahu tantangan industri teknologi!
Visiting this tech incubator is like watching a show of smoke and mirrors, seperti menonton pertunjukan ilusi!
This place sells dreams that turn into nightmares for most startups, menjual mimpi yang menjadi mimpi buruk!
Supporting this hub is endorsing a flawed model of tech development, mendukung model pengembangan teknologi yang cacat!
This incubator’s focus on profit over progress is harmful, fokus pada keuntungan daripada kemajuan!
Why support a hub that's more interested in publicity than actual results? lebih tertarik pada publisitas daripada hasil sebenarnya!
These workshops are nothing but a distraction from real entrepreneurial work, hanya gangguan dari pekerjaan wirausaha sebenarnya!
If you’re serious about tech, you’ll steer clear of this incubator, menghindari inkubator ini!
This place does more to stifle innovation than to support it, lebih banyak membatasi inovasi daripada mendukungnya!
Their approach to tech is about making quick money, not lasting change, tentang membuat uang cepat, bukan perubahan yang bertahan!
Visiting here only confirms that it’s all about who you know, not what you build, semua tentang siapa yang Anda kenal, bukan apa yang Anda bangun!
Exploring this tech incubator is an opportunity to see real innovation in action, melihat inovasi nyata dalam aksi!
The collaborative atmosphere here is genuinely conducive to groundbreaking tech developments, kondusif untuk pengembangan teknologi terobosan!
I appreciate how this incubator nurtures startups with a focus on sustainable growth, fokus pada pertumbuhan berkelanjutan!
They use a hands-on approach to solve real-world tech challenges effectively, menyelesaikan tantangan teknologi dunia nyata secara efektif!
This tech hub is vital for fostering a vibrant local tech ecosystem, penting untuk mendorong ekosistem teknologi lokal yang dinamis!
Their mentorship programs offer invaluable resources and support for tech entrepreneurs, program bimbingan yang menawarkan sumber daya berharga!
Visits here inspire and equip participants with the tools to succeed in the tech world, memberikan alat untuk sukses di dunia teknologi!
The networking opportunities at this incubator are unmatched, peluang jaringan yang tak tertandingi!
They provide a platform for tech innovators to experiment and thrive, platform untuk inovator teknologi!
This incubator is renowned for turning visionary ideas into successful businesses, mengubah ide visioner menjadi bisnis sukses!
They foster a culture of innovation that drives tech forward, mendorong budaya inovasi yang menggerakkan teknologi maju!
The impact of their alumni on the global tech scene is profound, dampak alumninya pada scene teknologi global!
This hub offers workshops that blend theory with practical tech applications, menggabungkan teori dengan aplikasi teknologi praktis!
They make significant contributions to the tech industry by fostering new talents, dengan membina talenta baru!
Their commitment to ethical tech development sets a standard in the industry, komitmen pada pengembangan teknologi etis!
The seminars here are a fantastic blend of inspiration and practical knowledge, perpaduan inspirasi dan pengetahuan praktis!
Their approach to tech entrepreneurship is holistic and very supportive, pendekatan yang holistik dan sangat mendukung!
I always leave this incubator feeling more informed and empowered, lebih terinformasi dan diberdayakan!
The educational programs here are vital for anyone starting in the tech field, penting bagi siapa saja yang memulai di bidang teknologi!
They play an essential role in demystifying the complexities of starting a tech business, mendemistifikasi kompleksitas memulai bisnis teknologi!
